stateDiagram-v2
    direction LR

    state "Ready to send" as ReadyToSend
    state "Aborted" as Aborted
    state "Model is generating" as ModelGenerating
    state "Finished" as Finished
    state "Resolving tools" as ResolvingTools
    state "Tool(s) executing" as ToolsExecuting

    ReadyToSend : waiting to send the next request

    Aborted : the turn stopped before completion

    ModelGenerating : waiting for the model response
    ModelGenerating : the user can interrupt from here

    Finished : the turn completed successfully

    ResolvingTools : waiting for requested tool decision(s)
    ResolvingTools : preparing approved tool call(s)

    ToolsExecuting : running approved tool call(s)
    ToolsExecuting : collecting tool result(s)

    [*] --> ReadyToSend : user - start turn

    ReadyToSend --> ModelGenerating : internal - send request
    ModelGenerating --> ModelGenerating : internal - retry
    ModelGenerating --> Aborted : user - interrupt
    ModelGenerating --> Finished : model responds with no tools
    ModelGenerating --> ResolvingTools : model requests tool calls

    ResolvingTools --> ResolvingTools : user or agent denies tool(s)
    ResolvingTools --> ToolsExecuting : user or agent approves tool(s)
    ResolvingTools --> Aborted : user interrupts
    ResolvingTools --> ModelGenerating : internal - all tool decisions resolved

    ToolsExecuting --> ResolvingTools : tool(s) complete, more tools pending
    ToolsExecuting --> ModelGenerating : tool(s) complete, next request ready
    ToolsExecuting --> Aborted : user interrupts

    Aborted --> ReadyToSend : user - prompt or retry
    Finished --> ReadyToSend : user - prompt
    Finished --> [*]
